title: Flashback to Ray J and Bow-wow interview and more
itunes:title: Flashback to Ray J and Bow-wow interview and more
description:
Today on the show we flashed back to when Bow- Wow and Ray J pulled up on them and gave them a hilarious interview, as they spoke about the party life, dating and new projects. Also, we flashed back to when Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the Maga Mob who stormed the capitol and how the officials handled the situation. And since it is Thursday we also flashed back to some classic callers from "Ask Yee" and "Ask C and E"
